<C>__{lieutenant}
<P>__{(sardonically)}
<D>__{oh, i see. he was having trouble and you were helping him out.}
<C>__{klaatu}
<P>__{(pleasantly)}
<D>__{that's right.}
<C>__{lieutenant}
<P>__{(quietly sharp and accusing)}
<D>__{i suppose you know that barnhardt does a lot of secret work for the army.}
