<D>__{in this case the secret wouldn't be worth much. he doesn't know the answer himself.}
<C>__{lieutenant}
<P>__{(growing impatient)}
<D>__{but i suppose you know the answer.}
<C>__{klaatu}
<P>__{(with a deprecating shrug)}
<D>__{it's really quite simple... the three body problem, you know.}
<A>__{the lieutenant shifts in his chair, annoyed that he has to deal with this madman. he glances at a report on his desk, trying to control his impatience.}
<C>__{lieutenant}
<D>__{your name's carpenter that right?}
<P>__{(klaatu nods)}
